      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "2021, encountered a missing <code>javax.swing.Icon</code> class. There is another step I need to do, which is to restart the IDE after removing the JRE system library, and do it before adding back in the required JRE system library (Java 16 for me)."
